QuestData.Title: Uncatalogued Species
QuestData.Description: Lauranna must've missed this particular plant. You're certain you've discovered a species not yet catalogued by Lauranna's work. You'd best show it to her to see what she makes of it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Uncatalogued Species to Lauranna Thar'well at the Cenarion Refuge in Zangarmarsh.
QuestData.CompletionText: You have something to show me?
QuestData.RewardText: A new species! Are you sure?$B$B<Lauranna flips through pages of notes and diagrams.>$B$BNice job, $N. We'll have to add this one to our list. How does "Purple Leafed $Nrium" sound to you? It does have a ring to it.
